commitResults.messageBody: Add filter command in user guide

Added schedule as a person field.
If date not present, treat as schedule not present.
If date not present, use min value of LocalDate.
If time not present, use midnight of LocalTime.
Update sample data, json, add and edit commands.

Update edit command to edit instead of using default value.
Update sample data to have varied date-time combinations.

For syntax of command, use sn/ sd/ st/ to deconflict with
n/ for name and t/ for tags.
Update schedule to include name of schedule.

When schedule command is only provided the index, clears the schedule.
If schedule command is provided at least one argument, replaces those
arguments in the existing schedule, but keeps the other arguments' values.
